{"tid":1961748,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【叫港人加油】「是非精」梁嘉琪無得留低 離TVB轉做網上賣衫","createTime":"2020-04-07T04:00:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T20:58:41.000Z","uid":21849,"like":71,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"a9546d25bf379a0d5b63571d71f077ae6e34d57d","tid":1961748,"uid":21849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T04:00:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">【叫港人加油】「是非精」梁嘉琪無得留低 離TVB轉做網上賣衫</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n梁嘉琪是無綫綜藝節目《學是學非》的大師姐，做足六輯，但來到最近播出的第七輯突然被飛出局。有傳她因為去年6月時曾於IG post了一張寫住「加油」字樣的黑白相，並寫道：「轉右90度看」，即變成了「香港」，為香港打氣，因此遭TVB雪藏。<br />\n<br />\n據悉嘉琪近月已靜悄悄離開工作13年的TVB，她昨日回覆《蘋果》未有透露正式的離職日期，暫時未定去向，她說：「不好意思，合約真的不方便透露了，但也非常感謝公司一直畀了很多機會讓大家認識我，有新工作一定會告訴大家的，謝謝你！」她表示現時會好好增值自己，並會趁現在放多些時間在網上的裙子生意，她續說：「演藝工作也安排中，但不好意思，暫未能透露住。」<br />\n<br />\n相信嘉琪的離開也是為勢所迫，去年11月出席活動時，被問到是否遭大台雪藏，她還叫大家放心：「我個人仲喺度，唔好嚇我，早前《學是學非》係停咗，但大家仲可以睇吓我其他工作，呢排經常周圍飛，又拍一啲網上旅遊節目，又拍吓廣告，遲啲飲食節目同泰國旅行節目會喺無綫播，我同無綫合約仲未約滿，咁所以大家可放心，仲可以見到我。」怎料不足半年，仍逃不過「被離職」命運，而J2台播出的《血併全世界》便為成嘉琪在TVB最後一個節目。<br />\n<br />\n現年38歲的梁嘉琪於2003年在香港演藝學院戲劇學院畢業，初出道時常被指貌似梁小冰，後來加入有線電視主持《怪談》節目，在一次戶外探鬼團中因畏懼大哭而一舉成名。有指梁嘉琪是經演藝班同學王祖藍引薦下於2007年加入無綫，與李佳芯和黃翠如被視為有線過檔無綫的三小花之一。大台高層余詠珊一直好睇重前有線藝人，梁嘉琪入無綫初期亦機會不絕，初次參演電視劇《學警狙擊》飾演花若葆（暱稱藥煲），之後再拍《師父&middot;明白了》、《愛我請留言》等，可惜被彈演技未夠班，反而主持《學是學非》憑生鬼表現獲得讚賞。嘉琪與黃心穎、李佳芯和麥美恩一齊主持第一輯《學是學非》，成為元祖級的「是非精」，但心穎因「安心偷食」事件復工無期，李佳芯又因叫人登記做選民而遭大陸網民封殺，現在只有麥美恩有得留低。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/EHT_Dzq4g-4785TK2-4JyL8Dwis=/802x451/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/TPJM553O2WDP7KSFPF5TL3VOSE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FEHT_Dzq4g-4785TK2-4JyL8Dwis%3D%2F802x451%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FTPJM553O2WDP7KSFPF5TL3VOSE.jpg&h=e84f1b7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/hA7Zw53OFxTGh0fzgvjTvlOP1vg=/802x965/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/AADGT7X426SEVOHDHDBLGW5BPE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FhA7Zw53OFxTGh0fzgvjTvlOP1vg%3D%2F802x965%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FAADGT7X426SEVOHDHDBLGW5BPE.jpg&h=eb1398c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/oGMEhBx5QO76b9z1ePy30ay25II=/802x735/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/4HCZS53EUKER5DT6ZSDHXTSZUQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FoGMEhBx5QO76b9z1ePy30ay25II%3D%2F802x735%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2F4HCZS53EUKER5DT6ZSDHXTSZUQ.jpg&h=da25f34e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/3_inCTnumcDL4G3ijdp2l9AZOJ4=/802x1426/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/VAKSNCAIA5IM6VCE4YEDVKB4FE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2F3_inCTnumcDL4G3ijdp2l9AZOJ4%3D%2F802x1426%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FVAKSNCAIA5IM6VCE4YEDVKB4FE.jpg&h=0fdc0c57&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e2fafb32c3945d49cdd5189aa622105fedaa69e","tid":1961748,"uid":49853,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T04:06:13.000Z","msg":"李佳芯都俾人雪左"},{"pid":"1cb798b749d7306b1d9d974939e3719d28d087e6","tid":1961748,"uid":81113,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T04:08:50.000Z","msg":"冇睇TVB就快1年"},{"pid":"7480ef098f7583724376e1b62061b243525ca368","tid":1961748,"uid":309148,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T04:09:49.000Z","msg":"佢之前做&lsquo;小報告&rsquo;個角色幾正 好似係同奶共王祖藍一齊拍嘅<br />\npush 撐黃藝人"},{"pid":"b0186e5a9059e9